task.summary: Default task
first prototype. client can now fetch JSON questions from server/database on page load. Freetext regex answers can be evaluated and checked against stored possible answers for that question
added express-stormpath module to handle user authentication and managing user data
now able to access user data on page load by passing a big chuck on JSON into the template render, REMEMBER to escape nubers in JSON object keys by using box notation!
lots of debugging! worked on getting game to save level progress and question data against user properly. Messed around with $.post for hours before realising I should use $.ajax

more debugging. added functions to pull total score and currentQscore and display on page, started working on calculating valid score without using localstorage, still needs work. added way more questions to database

reading and writing JSON to server is now better insync because of ajaxComplete() function, no more total_score problems. Game now saves score on each submission so player cannot reload question to get better score. Score is protected from going below zero. Completed levels now indicated as such on level chose page.

added misconception logging but correct and incorrect uncaught misconceptions refactored checkAnswer and added testRegex() which tests if the submitted answer actually works as a regular expression, but still then checks our misconceptions to see if we have caught it
not much added since last commit. Added custom feedback for the clause where player has submitted valid regex that we have not caught in our misconceptions

completed tests of checkAnser refactor and cleared up any bugs. Tested the logging of misconceptions and this is working now. implemented leaderboard first prototype. few small bug fixes. few small UI things. navbar now sets active the page li element it is on
fixed checkAnswer() logic bug, some if/else statements werent structured correctly. Then mainly implemented the progen prototype which is working well with difficulty slider
connected progen to points system and implemented scoring logic
pushing some new files I added, etxernal scripts and stypesheets and images
test commit after problems last thursday
test commit after problems last thursday
replaced localhost references with relative paths
few UI bits, added Arcade link. fixed a bit of scoring logic and added disabling of buttons

implemented start of badge mechanism. Badges are now rewarded for point thresholds. Bad mechanism implemented on server side where checks are performed and any new badges won are returned to client in http response, as JSON
tweaked badges so that they now work well with story mode as well. Created badge graphics so there are now pulled through to modals. Added badge display to stats page but this needs refining
server now rewards badges faster after removing loads of unecessary looping. Loads of UI tweaks, some bug fixing. Started working on admin screen and pulling question miusconception data.
worked on admin page. Database queries about question data now work on server and client side, this is pretty cool. That's it really, just made this work nicely, plenty of UI tweaks.
adding some files that were missed in last commit. bootstrap switch library and stylesheet
adding some files that were missed in last commit. bootstrap switch library and stylesheet
small UI changes to stormpath jade files, colro changes and styling etc
small color change to jade files
pushing badge image files

tuned up procedural generation engine and testing extensively. Changed scoring system so you get less points. Updated badge graphics. Fixed progen bugs so it always produces valid regex now, and sensible match and notmatch strings
added feedback form to layout hbs, this now submits feedback data to server and this is written to database
adding feedback-link image file
changed broder color on button. Possibly fixed multple appendation of msgbox bug
added some meta tags to layout.hbs adn also added a logo for open graph tags
no longer need ot be logged in to visit index page, appented template params as required
small bug following last commit
smal bug
committing new image files with background colour completely to alpha this time!
updated robot image for error page
fixed stupid json property name bug. thanks to user testing!
changes to app to run on port 80 if production environment. Improve register page UI and password requirements description
refer to bug list check off today. lots of bug fixing some small some big. Fixed huge hole in progen and tuned this back up again, ranges wern't being created correctly. scrollable table in stats etc

refer to bug fixing logs to see bugs fixed in this commit. some tasty UI bits. Fine tuned progen engine again and added a further regex check to remove space repetition at the end of expression e.g. ' {3}'
small updates
removed default checked radio buttons in feedback form. fixed login/logout bug

implemented the new levels recording system that stores levels in an array. this means you can now complete level 3 and it doesn't set your progress as if you have completed 1,2, and 3! includes changes to levelsChoose screen, stats screen, and recordUserProgress function. Needs testing
fixed bug in progen where space characters were not being translated to the HTML, these are now replaced with nbsp; Added badge gallery so players can see what's available.

added new feedback form that uses SUS industry standard testing, this is writing to new database collection. People now get a popup urging them to leave feedback, it goes away when they successfully do!
added robots.txt file
admin pages are now protected by admin user group auth. Fixed popover feedback bug to indicate which value was highest
